what i did
SM-02 video conference plan, meeting scenario (Sol Yun, Love Puppy, pullus)
The advertisement banner was exposed 5 times per person, and the price was measured at 135,000 won.
We have prepared a promotion that offers a 26% discount from 135,000 won to 100,000 won.
The scenario was prepared by buying and selling each company's items.
SM-03 Overseas Meeting Plan, Meeting Scenario (SANDY)
I prepared a scenario where I bought 5 earrings among SANDY's items and sold advertisement banners to SANDY.
SM-04 Understanding B2B and B2C Sales
B2B is simply business-to-business sales.
B2C is simply business-to-consumer sales.
SM-05 pre-sale (send email to SANDY team)
SM-06 Price Proposal and Pricing Strategy (Sol Yun, Love Puppy, pullus, SANDY)
We set a price strategy of discounting the price from 130,000 won to 100,000 won as a promotion by taking the average of 5 exposures per person.
what I learned
I know the exact difference between B2B and B2C.
I felt that strategic roles such as planning and promotion before meetings with companies were important.
Even when sending emails, I noticed that the flow in other countries and Korea is different.

